title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) in France 2024
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes GDP in billion U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 41.
Overall GDP in billion U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum GDP in billion U.S. dollars, about 3214.61 was reported at Year 2024
The lowest GDP in billion U.S. dollars, of value 532.34 was reported at Year 1984
